{"tid":2036703,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"求下你地聽日唔好開遮","createTime":"2020-05-26T15:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T17:26:19.000Z","uid":303304,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3aa109c22f8d3fe2d2ecaf5b54abb52060451fa","tid":2036703,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警察公共關係科總警司謝振中今日在警察記者會上提到，蒙面暴徒違法之時，一般情況下會聽到他們大叫：「落雨，要開遮！」，意即用雨傘去遮擋犯法過程；謝振中批評，暴徒們如此做，只顯示自己心虛、理虧，因他們自知所作所為有錯，害怕給記者和公眾拍下，令人見到他們醜惡、邪惡的一面。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好彩你地24號私了人同行動嗰陣冇開遮咋，如果唔係點影到邊個打邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6babecba94feb818803474b699ddbbc907024b","tid":2036703,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4412df9aff1ddf7896e335f05ff6ed0077add65e","tid":2036703,"uid":303304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e6babecba94feb818803474b699ddbbc907024b","tid":2036703,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:28:51.000Z","msg":"啱啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec77b487cc6bafd686b7c5a966dff5af407b9709","tid":2036703,"uid":108571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"天氣報告話聽日雷暴警告 會落雨"},{"pid":"102b0d0fc644afb8920ed1969b2a58de146f24ea","tid":2036703,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e6babecba94feb818803474b699ddbbc907024b","tid":2036703,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"block柒咗你先🤙🏻🤙🏻"},{"pid":"307f695b1a8d7d073cba82e3b44c14c6a35eae3b","tid":2036703,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec77b487cc6bafd686b7c5a966dff5af407b9709","tid":2036703,"uid":108571,"like":0,"dislik